How to Arrive\par
By Air: The nearest international airport is Rijeka Airport (RJK) on the island of Krk, approximately 40 km (25 miles) away. Other options include Pula Airport (PUY) at 100 km (62 miles) and Zagreb Airport (ZAG) at 180 km (112 miles), offering more international connections.\par
\par
By Train: Opatija-Matulji train station (5 km from center) is the main rail hub. From there, taxis or local buses provide easy access to Opatija. Rijeka's larger train station (15 km away) offers more connections.\par
\par
By Car: Opatija is well-connected by Croatia's modern highway network. Follow signs for Rijeka, then Opatija. Main routes include the A7 (Rupa-Rijeka) and A6/A1 from Zagreb or Split.\par
